reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Enough cushion for good support but not too much to raise you up too high
reviews.reviewText: Got this for those long, 10+ hour car trips, where having a nice supportive cushion means making less stops to stretch legs and get blood flowing. Worked great. I appreciate that it comes with buckles in the back to prevent it from sliding around, and other than when it's left in the sun it feels quite cool to the touch.
